Build the adapter compatibility matrix:

ADAPTER_MATRIX = {
    "c3600" : {                     # Router model
        "3620" : {                  # Router chassis (if applicable)
            { 0 : ("NM-1FE-TX", "NM_1E", ...)
            }
        }
    }

This will generate replacement string for
{port0} => {port9}
{segment0} => {segment9}
